name: Delly Welly's Procedural Parade
description:
"Here we have it, Delly Welly's fabulous parade generator for your very own personal computer! We have ever spawning generated characters created for your eyes only, never to be seen again! Wonder in the miracle of software engineering at its most pioneering as the paradees navigate the obstacle course using cutting edge procedural animation technology! 
Welcome my friends, to the Parade!"
